com.philips.pins.shinelib

Interface SHNAssociationProcedure


  • public interface SHNAssociationProcedure
    A placeholder interface for SHNDeviceAssociation. Provides better type safety over using Object. SHNAssociationProcedure is reported to the user of API via SHNDeviceAssociation.SHNDeviceAssociationListener.onAssociationStarted(SHNAssociationProcedure) callback. Returned instance is not type strong. The API user needs to caste it to the proper class type.
